        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 12 at 12:43PM EDT by NWS Blacksburg VA</headline>
        <description>At 1242 PM EDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Maple Springs, or near Wilbar, moving east at 10 mph.

HAZARD...Pea size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...

Locations impacted include...
Wilkesboro...
Wilbar...
Mulberry...
Cricket...
Wilkesboro Reservoir...
Buck...
and Cascade Falls.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
